<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="W" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Wittingly" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Wittingly,</orth> with knowledge, by design, on purpose: <cit><quote>nor w. have I infringed my vow,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 3h6 2.2.8" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C II, 2, 8</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>if I drown myself w.</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 5.1.11" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. V, 1, 11</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. ham 5.1.11" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. V, 1, 11</bibl> cf. <emph>Unwittingly.</emph>
